 <text>
  <front>
   <head>TO RUIN.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="tetrameter">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">ALL hail! inexorable lord!</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">At whose destruction-breathing word,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The mightiest empires fall!</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Thy cruel, woe-delighted train,</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The ministers of Grief and Pain,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">A sullen welcome, all!</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">With stern-resolv'd, despairing eye,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">I see each aimed dart;</l>
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">For one has cut my dearest tye,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And quivers in my heart.</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Then low'ring, and pouring,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The Storm no more I dread;</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Tho' thick'ning, and black'ning,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Round my devoted head.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="tetrameter">
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And thou grim Pow'r, by Life abhorr'd,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">While Life a pleasure can afford,</l>
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Oh! hear a wretch's pray'r!</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">No more I shrink appall'd, afraid;</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">I court, I beg thy friendly aid,</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To close this scene of care!</l>
     <l n="21" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">When shall my soul, in silent peace,</l>
     <l n="22" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Resign Life's joyless day?</l>
     <l n="23" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">My weary heart it's throbbings cease,</l>
     <l n="24" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Cold-mould'ring in the clay?</l>
     <l n="25" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">No fear more, no tear more,</l>
     <l n="26" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To stain my lifeless face,</l>
     <l n="27" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Enclasped, and grasped,</l>
     <l n="28" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Within thy cold embrace!</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
